&lt;p&gt;Since then I published 130 more articles and notes and one even explains why this site is named &lt;a href=&quot;https://justmarkup.com/log/2018/11/just-markup/&quot;&gt;justmarkup&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
